OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780002672
OL,3,CJudge told boy rapists 'akin' to past
OL,4,Ccase of teenager jailed for eight years
OL,6,FThe judge who did not jail three boy
OL,7,Frapists was advised by the prosecution
OL,8,Fcounsel that the offences were "akin"
OL,9,Fto a previous case where a teenage
OL,10,Frapist was given an eight-year
OL,11,Fcustodial sentence, the Press
OL,12,FAssociation has learned.
OL,14,FTwo 15-year-olds were given non-
OL,15,Fcustodial sentences after raping two
OL,16,Fgirls in Fordingbridge, Hampshire, by
OL,17,FJudge Nicholas Rowland at Southampton
OL,18,FCrown Court, who said he wanted to
OL,19,F"avoid criminalising these children
OL,20,Funnecessarily".
OL,26,@pD@`OUpD@eO]{D@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
