OL,3,CJudge told boy rapists 'akin' to past
OL,4,Ccase of teenager jailed for eight years
OL,6,FIn an interview with the BBC's Sunday
OL,7,FWith Laura Kuenssberg programme, the
OL,8,Fother victim, now 16, said of the
OL,9,Fboys' sentence: "The words hit like a
OL,10,Frock straight in my face."
